{"tid":480890,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】之前話想玩隻Game出左  Day153 25/11","createTime":"2017-11-26T15:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T16:13:45.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5c16db4082b2acf5ac724f4250e4d8eb482a0dd1","tid":480890,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=KZYbFxoQu%2F8EMKMvt%2Bmsoi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=890cb71c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=KZYbFxoQu%2F8EMKMvt%2Bmsoi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3297ddeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"a0509ee07154716b0a4d38ba80b17d284fad300f","tid":480890,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f2e922e209c95ac86c97d051b7df581fb77c66","tid":480890,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcec2cac56c5b36ebe499fbb902ceb42f52dcb34","ti